   <div class="article_content" id="bxdk_article_content">
    <p class="rich_media_content" id="js_content"><img data-ratio="0.11875" data-type="gif" data-w="640" data-src="http://7xu6d7.com2.z0.glb.qiniucdn.com/article_upload_pic_1490598924" style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: center; white-space: pre-wrap; visibility: visible !important; width: auto !important;" width="auto" src="http://7xu6d7.com2.z0.glb.qiniucdn.com/article_upload_pic_1490598924" /><br /><img data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" data-src="http://7xu6d7.com2.z0.glb.qiniucdn.com/article_upload_pic_1490598925" data-ratio="0.2242152466367713" data-w="669" src="http://7xu6d7.com2.z0.glb.qiniucdn.com/article_upload_pic_1490598925" /><br /></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">俗话说：满堂儿女不如半路夫妻。但3月22日，成都商报报道的一则新闻却讲述了一对半路夫妻相爱相杀后，只剩下遍体鳞伤的爱情、因无钱医治而正饱受癌症折磨的身体及为了讨说法而不得不一次次奔波的官司。</p> 
    <br />
    <section data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="86412" data-color="#086070" style=""> 
     <section style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"> 
      <section style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"> 
       <section style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"> 
        <section class="" data-source="bj.96weixin.com" style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"> 
         <section style=""> 
          <section class="" style="margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; padding: 10px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; border-top-width: 3px; border-top-style: solid; border-top-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); border-left-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(229, 229, 229); line-height: 30px; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-weight: 700; text-align: center; border-right-color: rgb(239, 112, 96); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"> 
           <span style=""></span> 
           <span style=""></span> 
           <span style=""></span> 
           <span style=""></span> 
           <span style="">七年内他转给妻子70余万元，他生病了，妻子账上却没钱了！</span> 
          </section> 
         </section> 
        </section> 
        <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">2005年，四川省成都市青白江区居民张先生和胡女士结婚。两人均属再婚，婚后没有生育子女。张先生现年51岁，胡女士比他小4岁。</span><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p> 
       </section> 
      </section> 
     </section> 
    </section>
    <br /> 
    <p style=""><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p> 
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">张先生平时帮人做工程，四处奔波。由于懂化工，外出打工期间收入可观。“大多数时候，月收入都会过万。”</p> 
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p> 
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">至少从2010年起，每月领到工资后，张先生除了留点零花钱外，都会悉数转入胡女士的银行账户中。银行流水显示，胡女士的两张银行卡先后收到过张先生转入的约60笔现金,总数达78万左右。“2010年前，我也是按月把工资转给妻子。结婚以来，我转给她的钱应在100万左右。”</p> 
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p> 
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">不幸的是，去年9月，张先生<strong style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">患上了前列腺癌晚期</strong>。在筹措手术费时，妻子却告诉他家里没钱了。张先生妹妹表示，由于哥哥按月将工资转给妻子，“生病时，他自己的银行卡内仅有1万余元。去年哥哥做手术一共花费6万余元。我借了5万给他。”张先生统计，从去年9月6日检查出前列腺癌到今年2月27日，各种费用已花去9万余元。“我已向妹妹借了10万元。”</p> 
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img data-ratio="0.6171875" data-s="300,640" data-type="png" data-w="640" data-src="http://7xu6d7.com2.z0.glb.qiniucdn.com/article_upload_pic_1490598926" style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: 100%; visibility: visible !important; height: auto;" width="auto" src="http://7xu6d7.com2.z0.glb.qiniucdn.com/article_upload_pic_1490598926" /></p> 
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">因为妻子拒绝支付医疗费，张先生将妻子告上法庭，除请求离婚外，同时还请求法院对夫妻二人的债权债务进行分割。</span><span style="max-width: 100%; line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">“<strong style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">离婚不是我的目的，但确实是没钱治病啊！</strong>”</span></p> 
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p> 
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">诉讼期间，法院调取了胡女士名下的银行账号，发现账户内余额仅有300余元。另外所有的证券、股票加起来，价值也不过数千元。这一切让张先生感到非常奇怪。张先生介绍，两人结婚后，他们于2006年按揭购买了一套房子，“当时每月月供仅有600余元。另外妻子从原公司下岗后，也得到了一笔近十万元的补偿金。”</p> 
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p> 
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">法庭上，胡女士表示，双方婚姻关系存续期间，张先生确实将部分收入交给她管理，“但在双方的共同生活中已经全部消费了。”对此，张先生提出了质疑，“就我的了解，对方（胡女士）是一个极为俭省的人。<span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">我转给她的70多万，咋能说没就没了呢？</span>”</p> 
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p> 
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">由于双方均一致同意离婚，一审法院判决准许两人离婚。两人一致认可共同所有房屋价值34万。住房归胡女士所有，但胡女士需支付张先生房屋折价款15万余元。</p> 
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p> 
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">因对一审判决不服，张先生现已提起上诉，希望法院能够查明胡女士相关银行账户的流水明细，同时，张先生妹妹也以张先生、胡女士二人作为共同被告提起诉讼，试图讨回之前自己给哥哥垫付的医药费。</p> 
    <br />
    <section class="" data-source="bj.96weixin.com" style=""> 
     <section style=""> 
      <section class="" style="margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; padding: 10px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; border-top-width: 3px; border-top-style: solid; border-top-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); border-left-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(229, 229, 229); line-height: 30px; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-weight: 700; text-align: center; border-right-color: rgb(239, 112, 96); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"> 
       <span style="">男人，爱没错，但要看人！记得给自己留条后路，以免遍体鳞伤！</span> 
      </section> 
     </section> 
    </section>
    <br /> 
    <p style=""><strong style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">凡事给自己留一条后路，遇到困难时才会有一条出路！让自己有一个回旋的余地。</span></strong><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p> 
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p> 
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">在婚姻里，<span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">不只女性要懂得给自己留一条退路，不把全部的赌注都押在婚姻上面，男性亦然！</span>因为任何婚姻都是有风险的，要懂得把风险的概率缩小化。因此要在婚姻以外的东西上投入时间和精力，以期即便有变故，也不会伤筋动骨！</p> 
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p> 
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">婚姻以外的东西有什么？事业、社交圈、学习、特长爱好、友人、亲人等等。每一项都是需要花费时间和精力去精进和维护。而这之外，还有一种单据必须拥有并保存，那就是――保单！一张确保在意外、疾病等人生风险发生之后第一时间能够给予自己一大笔救命钱、应急钱的保险合同！不用背负什么人情债，且专款专用，不受婚姻状况影响，不被任何人所支配、挪用！</p> 
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img data-ratio="0.75" data-s="300,640" data-type="png" data-w="640" data-src="http://7xu6d7.com2.z0.glb.qiniucdn.com/article_upload_pic_1490598927" style="line-height: 25.6px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: 100%; visibility: visible !important; height: auto;" width="auto" src="http://7xu6d7.com2.z0.glb.qiniucdn.com/article_upload_pic_1490598927" /><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p> 
    <br />
    <section class="" data-source="bj.96weixin.com" style=""> 
     <section style=""> 
      <section class="" style="margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; padding: 10px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; border-top-width: 3px; border-top-style: solid; border-top-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); border-left-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(229, 229, 229); line-height: 30px; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-weight: 700; text-align: center; border-right-color: rgb(239, 112, 96); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"> 
       <span style=""></span> 
       <span style="">吃不穷穿不穷，不会盘算才受穷！别对保险嗤之以鼻，男人真的更需要！</span> 
      </section> 
     </section> 
    </section>
    <br /> 
    <p style=""><strong style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">1、健康风险大，但对体检不重视！</span></strong></p> 
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">《中国人身保险业重大疾病经验发生率表（2006－2010）》显示，重大疾病的发病率，随年龄递增而不断升高，步入中年的疾病高发期后，同年龄的男性发病率明显高于女性。</p> 
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p> 
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">资料表明，每年国内约有100万名男性发生心脏病，35岁以下的男性患高血压的风险远高于女性。此外，《发生率》数据显示，25种重疾险男性致死最高的年龄为59岁，致死率超过60%为49-78岁之间。</p> 
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p> 
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">但值得注意的是，男性看病的频率要比女性低28%，20%的男性从来不参加任何形式的体育锻炼，80%的重病男性患者承认自己是因为长期不去医院就诊，面对小病小痛，都喜欢忍着，总以为熬一熬就会好了。殊不知，很多大病都是这样“熬”出来的。一旦得了大病，就会影响到工作、影响到收入，甚至将父母的养老钱花光、将子女的教育金花没。</p> 
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p> 
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">2、意外几率高，但保险意识差！</strong></p> 
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">目前全球男性和女性的平均寿命差距越来越大，男性的预期寿命要比女性短6年。这是由于男性普遍有着不良生活习惯，如抽烟、酗酒等，而且男性的精神压力和意外事故发生率都高于女性。</p> 
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p> 
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">但即便如此，主动投保的男性不多，据最近一份调查显示，74%的受访女性愿意为自己购买各种保险产品，用以提供疾病、意外等保障；而受访男性中，这一比例仅占61%。</p> 
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p> 
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">“我帮我老公咨询了好几次保险，但他每次都不耐烦。”成都市民李女士表示，为了给30岁的老公提供一份保障，李女士在数次说服无果的情况下，只能“先斩后奏”，瞒着爱人给他上了一份保险，“他就觉得自己身体很健康，不用花这个钱。”</p> 
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p> 
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">3、男人只顾拼命赚钱，但忽略守钱！</strong></p> 
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">上述新闻所提到的张先生就是一个典型案例！挣了钱转手就给了妻子，由她打理，从此不闻不问，除非真的需要用钱了，殊不知他忽视了婚姻风险！</p> 
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p> 
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">即便婚姻没有变故，谁又能保证人生没有变故？疾病、意外可都是不请自来的两大瘟神，如果没有保险保障，一辈子的积蓄很可能都拱手送给了医院，甚至因此债台高筑！</p> 
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p> 
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">……</p> 
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p> 
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">婚姻，本就是一纸合约，用情时，它像冬天里的一盏热茶，暖的是身，一旦情义褪去，茶凉了，再喝，伤的是心。在此，<strong style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">惟愿天下夫妻都能在婚姻之外再签一纸合约――保险合同，情在时，它能锦上添花，情走时，它能雪中送炭！</span></strong></p> 
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p> 
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">我们不否认现在自己很幸福，但也要慢慢学会为自己留一条后路，就像保险：不用的时候，是持续增长的储蓄金；急用的时候，是流动资金和高额风险保障金；孩子长大的时候，是教育、创业、婚嫁储备金；年迈的时候，是安享晚年高额养老金；不在的时候，是规避税债的高额遗产金……</p> 
    <p style="text-align: right;"><span style="color: rgb(214, 214, 214); font-size: 12px;">来源：寿险天地</span><img data-ratio="0.0265625" data-s="300,640" data-src="http://7xu6d7.com2.z0.glb.qiniucdn.com/article_upload_pic_1490598928" data-type="png" data-w="640" style="font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 34.125px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible !important; width: 640px !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" width="auto" src="http://7xu6d7.com2.z0.glb.qiniucdn.com/article_upload_pic_1490598928" /></p> 
